-Dao, T (2550) Goodricke op 11th Kolkata 2000 (6) After something natural like}
Rb8 $36 {Black's position is more pleasant.}) 10... exd5 11. exd5 Nc5 $1 {
This basically refutes White's idea, but only due to the queen's position on
