postponed the serious study of a good antidote against 6.Bg5, was always
supported by the excuse that there were too many lines to memorize and
remember during the game. So it was a pleasant surprise to find out that in
this variation I had to remember fewer lines than I first thought.} Qxb2 10.
Rb1 (10. Nb3 $6 {is an option in the classic Poisoned Pawn, but here it
