} 22. Ne3 Rc8 23. b4 Qc7 $19 {[%cal Ya6a5,Gf6e7,Gd7f6] ;0-1 Kleijn, C (2383)
-Rumjantsev, J (2039) Wch U18 Kemer 2009 (2) and Black's position is already
winning.}) 20... Qc7 21. Rd3 Nb6 $17 {0-1 Nisipeanu, L (2668)-Karjakin, S 
(2694) World Cup Khanty-Mansiysk 2007 (4.2) While White's attacking ideas
