converted his advantage with nice technique.}) (11. h3 {was tried by a few
strong players, including some recent games. It doesn't seem so dangerous, but
let's check it anyway.} O-O 12. g4 (12. f5 $5 {seems more critical. Here it's
important to remember that} Bxb3 $1 {is the right reply.} ({Instead,} 12... Bc4
