½-½ Jakovenko, D (2722)-Karjakin, S (2785) RUS-ch 65th Moscow 2012 (6) and
Black is ok.}) 17. a3 $5 {White tries to get an advantage by preparing a
subtle idea. The following game is an instructive example of how to play as
