$6 {leaves White in trouble after the simple reply} Be7 $1 {[%cal Gf6e4,Ge7h4]
as White doesn't have an adequate way of dealing with the threat of Nxe4.
White needs to be very concrete here in order to keep the balance:} 11. Bxf6 ({
