O-O $1 15. Nxa8 Rd8 16. Qa5 Qxa5+ 17. Nxa5 exf4 {[%cal Gf6c3]} 18. Nb3 b5 $1 {
[%cal Gc8b7]} 19. Be2 {Weichhold,P (2428)-Sadzikowski,D (2548) POL-chT Poland
2017 (6.3) 1-0 Black could have achieved a winning advantage now by means of}
Bxa1 20. Nxa1 Bb7 21. Bf3 Bxf3 22. gxf3 Nd7 23. Nc7 Nc5 {[%csl Rc7] when the
