Nxa6 Ra8 $19) 12... Qa3 13. Nb6 Bxa1 14. Nxa1 Qc5 $5 15. Nxa8 b6 {[%csl Ra8]
Black regains the knight. After} 16. Bd3 Nd7 17. Nb3 Qc6 18. Qb4 O-O $1 19.
Nxb6 Nxb6 $11 {the position is balanced.}) 10... Qa3 11. e5 {The most
principled and more popular option.} (11. f5 {is another critical line. Black
