Qf2 $1 Nc6 $1 {Develop should come in first place here.} (18... Qxc4 $2 {
is a mistake as after} 19. Qf7+ Kd8 20. Qxg7 Re8 21. Rf7 Nd7 22. Rxb7 $1 $40 {
