{After finishing the development White has an interesting active idea:} 13. f5
$5 e5 14. Ne6 $1 fxe6 15. fxe6 Nc5 16. Rxf6 $1 {White sacrifices first a piece
and then an exchange in order to keep the black king in the centre. After} gxf6
17. Bh5+ {I consider} Kd8 $1 {the safest reply. White continues with} 18. Bxf6
{but here we have} Nxe6 $1 {[%cal Ga3d6] giving back the material. After} 19.
Bxh8 Bg5 $1 20. Qe1 Nf4 $132 {[%cal Gc8e6,Ga8c8] ;Hartmann,G-Huenerkopf,H
