} 16. Be2 (16. c3 $5 {was an interesting idea used by Caruana at the 2020-21
Candidates Tournament. The point is that after} Bc5 {White plays} 17. Bg3 Qd5
18. Bc4 $3 Qxc4 19. Bd6 $1 {[%csl Re8] A creative piece sacrifice which aims
to keep the enemy king in the centre. At the same time, Black starts to face
