} 22. Ndxe6 $1 fxe6 23. Nxe6 {when Black's position still looks scary. However,
the cold-blooded} Nf6 $3 {solves all the problems.} 24. Nf8+ (24. Nxg7+ $2 Kf7
25. Rf1 {seems strong, but we have the nice reply} Qxf1+ $1 26. Kxf1 Nc6 $17 {
[%csl Re5][%cal Gg8g7] ;Siva, M (2349)-Quintiliano Pinto, R (2469) Titled
